	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The textual authority for these names is uncertain. Manlius is an emendation of Manios, so that it is at least possible that M'. Sergius of no. b is meant (RE locc. citt.)." .
